parameters.name: YRDAY
parameters.description:
Real number containing year (19YY) and the day of
                        year (DDD) in the form (YYDDD.0).

parameters.name: MSEC
parameters.description:
Real number containing time in milliseconds of day
                        from 0.0 to 86400000.0.
